King Stephen - St. Stephen 1st King of Hungary AR Denar, EF, of "Holy Hand" fame, see notes, 997 - 1038 C.E.





KING STEPHAN AR SILVER DENAR Rethy 1, Toned Extremely Fine, 17.3mm, .64gram. Struck 997 - 1038 C.E., photo of obverse and reverse below.   The  FIRST coin of Hungary in EXCELLENT condition!  A RARE type issued by the First King who brought  Christianity to  Hungary and was later cannonized. His right hand is now  an icon as can  be seen HERE. 







