1.0 out of 5 starsPoor way to end a great series.ByDeweyon January 30, 2015Really disappointing. I expected the ending from pretty much the first book but the way he takes you there is sorely lacking in Kingishness. The book felt rushed - like he "had to" finish it. Book 6 was the same way. The first 5 books took years to write because he only wrote them when he was inspired. These last 2 he forced and you can tell.

